Tuuti CMS
---------

Tuuti CMS aims to be easy to use for common internet users. Think of your mother
or your uncle... The power under this tool is it's multilanguage ability. When
you don't have time to translate all your content, the engine select the 
language of the page based on languages priority configured.

Q: Who is the author of this fabulous piece of software ?
A: It's ADA Consultants Inc. from Quebec City, Canada.

Q: Why another CMS ?
A: Because at the time we started this project, we couldn't find any CMS that
   fitted our need. We wanted it to be simple and to be multilingual.

Q: What's the meaning of Tuuti ?
A: Tuuti is a word in Wolof that means "a little" or "small".